gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 129, Wizards 118
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Wizards, 129-118. Stephen Curry recorded 30 points (8-13 3PM) and seven assists for the Warriors, with Jonathan Kuminga adding 22 points, four rebounds, and three assists in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied 25 points, three rebounds, and three assists for the Wizards in the loss. The Warriors improve to 14-14 in the regular season, while the Wizards fall to 5-23.
